{"tid":1242574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋 果 可 唔 可 以 唔 好 再 用 蝗 字?","createTime":"2019-06-19T06:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T06:51:20.000Z","uid":61511,"like":66,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ce4b56953df3db833da53338b14c0339adcb44b1","tid":1242574,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:00:47.000Z","msg":"以前d人就話網上睇唔洗錢仲想點 都係既,錢又無俾,又多多要求<br />\n<br />\n好啦而家收錢了,可唔可以改返d用字?<br />\n唔係好高難度姐...下嘛?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【6.8級地震】新潟民眾慌忙戶外逃生 <span style=\"color: red;\">內地</span>網民：整個樓都在搖晃<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190618/59732583\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190618%2F59732583&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=3e8e5622\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190618%2F59732583&h=cbea16a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190618/59732583</a><br />\n<br />\n【公院亂局】醫委會研改善海外醫生執業試 臨床考核只需重考不及格科目<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190607/59677002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190607%2F59677002&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=d4c09ef5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190607%2F59677002&h=f2bafe3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190607/59677002</a><br />\n據悉，醫委會研究改善執業資格試，是希望令海外醫生與本地醫科生的考試模式看齊，令執業資格試模式更公平。現時獲<span style=\"color: red;\">內地</span>醫生資格的考生，於執業資格試及格率偏低，有委員表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">優化</span>措施理論上有助提升整體及格率，「不過如果係叻嘅，（考）一次都pass（及格）」，強調沒有降低對醫生質素要求。<br />\n<br />\n同場加映<br />\n【回歸廿年】熱選十大難頂大陸字　你揀嗰個有冇份？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170702/20075450\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170702%2F20075450&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=f11f57c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170702%2F20075450&h=644b8c24\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170702/20075450</a><br />\n「我哋要抓緊機遇」、「打造香港為世界級城市」、「做大做強」、「加大發展力度」、「重中之重」&hellip;&hellip;其實，何謂「做大做強」？「加大力度」不就是「加強」嗎？還有日常生活聽到的「小三」、「沙拉」、「一次性餐具」&hellip;&hellip;香港中文，何時變了樣？早前記者在本報Facebook做了一次「十大難頂大陸用字」調查：由蘋果讀者留言列出討厭字詞，我們則點算出現次數，結果留言竟多達三千多！讓我們現在揭曉結果，看大家最討厭的字詞是甚麼？"},{"pid":"c61d06d402969046ccfcc858da31b3d0073df9a1","tid":1242574,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b9fc6d6d60dd9f356f4064da118f586cd5baf3","tid":1242574,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2a1668ee90e0da27cc3f6a16ed405ee402c618","tid":1242574,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0465fe8992b9ef34c0f13d6ec075d68bc0b4952","tid":1242574,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bbbabb76cc57d9142fbcbe106dfa1b6b5ccd58","tid":1242574,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6e4309be78c5ffa96fe2cdef5084e23fa4311433","tid":1242574,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:35:59.000Z","msg":